<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>PrepSphere — AI Mock Interview Platform</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Rajdhani:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg:     #050816;
      --bg2:    #0a0f2e;
      --bg3:    #0d1433;
      --blue:   #00d4ff;
      --purple: #7b2ff7;
      --pink:   #ff006e;
      --green:  #00ff88;
      --yellow: #ffaa00;
      --white:  #ffffff;
      --gray:   #8892b0;
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--white);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* BG */
    .bg-fixed {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
      background:
        radial-gradient(700px 700px at 80% 10%, rgba(123,47,247,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(600px 600px at 10% 80%, rgba(0,212,255,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%),
        #050816;
    }
    .bg-grid {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0,212,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,212,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
      animation: gridPan 30s linear infinite;
    }
    @keyframes gridPan { to { background-position: 60px 60px; } }
    .scanlines {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 1; pointer-events: none;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 3px, rgba(0,212,255,0.004) 3px, rgba(0,212,255,0.004) 4px);
    }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding: 18px 60px;
      background: rgba(5,8,22,0.85);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.07);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-logo-badge {
      width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 900; color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,212,255,0.3);
    }
    .nav-logo-text {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
    }
    .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 36px; }
    .nav-link {
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--gray); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .nav-link:hover { color: var(--blue); }
    .nav-login {
      padding: 9px 22px; border-radius: 8px;
      background: rgba(0,212,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.3);
      color: var(--blue); font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .nav-login:hover {
      background: rgba(0,212,255,0.18);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,212,255,0.25);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      position: relative; z-index: 5;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 120px 40px 80px;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 6px 18px; border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(123,47,247,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(123,47,247,0.3);
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: #c084fc; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      animation: fadeDown 0.8s ease both;
    }
    .badge-dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--purple);
      animation: blink 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes blink { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0.3} }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-weight: 900;
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      animation: fadeDown 0.8s ease 0.1s both;
    }
    .hero-title .line1 { display: block; color: var(--white); }
    .hero-title .line2 {
      display: block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple), var(--pink));
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--gray); max-width: 600px;
      line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 48px;
      animation: fadeDown 0.8s ease 0.2s both;
    }
    .hero-sub span { color: var(--blue); font-weight: 600; }

    .hero-ctas {
      display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
      animation: fadeDown 0.8s ease 0.3s both;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 12px; border: none;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
      color: white; font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,212,255,0.3);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn-primary::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: -100%; width: 100%; height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), transparent);
      transition: 0.5s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,212,255,0.45); }
    .btn-primary:hover::before { left: 100%; }
    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(0,212,255,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.25);
      color: var(--blue); font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(0,212,255,0.12);
      border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.5);
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0,212,255,0.2);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    /* HERO STATS */
    .hero-stats {
      display: flex; gap: 60px; justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.4s both;
    }
    .stat { text-align: center; }
    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
    }
    .stat-label { font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--gray); letter-spacing: 2px; margin-top: 4px; }

    /* FLOATING CARDS */
    .hero-visual {
      position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; overflow: hidden; z-index: 2;
    }
    .float-card {
      position: absolute; padding: 14px 18px; border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(10,15,46,0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.15);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem;
      animation: floatCard ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes floatCard {
      0%,100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
    }
    .fc1 { top: 22%; left: 5%; animation-duration: 6s; animation-delay: 0s; color: var(--green); border-color: rgba(0,255,136,0.2); }
    .fc2 { top: 35%; right: 5%; animation-duration: 7s; animation-delay: 1s; color: var(--blue); }
    .fc3 { bottom: 25%; left: 8%; animation-duration: 5.5s; animation-delay: 0.5s; color: #c084fc; border-color: rgba(123,47,247,0.25); }
    .fc4 { bottom: 30%; right: 7%; animation-duration: 8s; animation-delay: 1.5s; color: var(--yellow); border-color: rgba(255,170,0,0.2); }
    .fc-label { font-size: 0.6rem; opacity: 0.5; margin-bottom: 4px; letter-spacing: 1px; }

    /* SECTION */
    section { position: relative; z-index: 5; }
    .section-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 100px 40px; }
    .section-tag {
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--blue); letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .section-sub { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--gray); max-width: 560px; line-height: 1.7; }

    /* HOW IT WORKS */
    .how-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; margin-top: 60px;
    }
    .step-card {
      background: var(--bg3); border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px 28px;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .step-card::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
    }
    .step-card:nth-child(1)::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--purple)); }
    .step-card:nth-child(2)::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--purple), var(--pink)); }
    .step-card:nth-child(3)::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--green), var(--blue)); }
    .step-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.2); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
    .step-num {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900;
      opacity: 0.08; position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 20px; line-height: 1;
      color: var(--blue);
    }
    .step-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .step-title { font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .step-desc { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; }

    /* FEATURES */
    .features-wrap { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center; margin-top: 60px; }
    .feature-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
    .feature-item {
      display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 20px 22px; border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(0,212,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.07);
      transition: all 0.3s ease; cursor: default;
    }
    .feature-item:hover { background: rgba(0,212,255,0.06); border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.18); transform: translateX(6px); }
    .feature-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
    .feature-title { font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .feature-desc { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.5; }

    /* MOCK TERMINAL */
    .mock-terminal {
      background: rgba(5,8,22,0.95);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    .terminal-bar {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      background: rgba(0,212,255,0.04);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.08);
    }
    .t-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .t-dot.red { background: #ff5f57; } .t-dot.yellow { background: #febc2e; } .t-dot.green { background: #28c840; }
    .terminal-title { font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--gray); margin-left: 8px; }
    .terminal-body { padding: 24px; font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 2; }
    .t-ai { color: var(--purple); }
    .t-user { color: var(--blue); }
    .t-system { color: var(--gray); opacity: 0.6; }
    .t-score { color: var(--green); }
    .t-cursor {
      display: inline-block; width: 8px; height: 14px;
      background: var(--blue); animation: cursorBlink 1s step-end infinite; vertical-align: middle;
    }
    @keyframes cursorBlink { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0} }

    /* MODES */
    .modes-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 20px; margin-top: 60px; }
    .mode-card {
      border-radius: 16px; padding: 36px 28px; text-align: center;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .mode-card::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .mode-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); }
    .mode-card:hover::after { border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.3); }
    .mode-card.explain { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,212,255,0.06), rgba(0,212,255,0.02)); }
    .mode-card.interview { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(123,47,247,0.08), rgba(123,47,247,0.02)); }
    .mode-card.both { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,0,110,0.07), rgba(255,0,110,0.02)); }
    .mode-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .mode-name { font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .mode-card.explain .mode-name { color: var(--blue); }
    .mode-card.interview .mode-name { color: #c084fc; }
    .mode-card.both .mode-name { color: var(--pink); }
    .mode-desc { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; }

    /* CTA SECTION */
    .cta-section {
      position: relative; z-index: 5;
      text-align: center; padding: 120px 40px;
    }
    .cta-glow {
      position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
      width: 600px; height: 400px; pointer-events: none;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(123,47,247,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    }
    .cta-title {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 20px; position: relative;
    }
    .cta-sub { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 48px; position: relative; }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      position: relative; z-index: 5;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.07);
      padding: 40px 60px;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    }
    .footer-logo { font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray); letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .footer-copy { font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgba(136,146,176,0.4); letter-spacing: 1px; }

    /* ANIMATIONS */
    @keyframes fadeDown { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(-20px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }
    @keyframes fadeUp   { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(20px);  } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }

    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease; }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    /* DIVIDER */
    .section-divider {
      position: relative; z-index: 5;
      height: 1px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0,212,255,0.1), transparent);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero { padding: 100px 24px 60px; }
      .how-grid, .modes-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .features-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-stats { gap: 36px; }
      .float-card { display: none; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; padding: 28px; }
      .section-inner { padding: 70px 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="bg-fixed"></div>
<div class="bg-grid"></div>
<div class="scanlines"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
    <div class="nav-logo-badge">PS</div>
    <div class="nav-logo-text">PREPSPHERE</div>
  </a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#how" class="nav-link">HOW IT WORKS</a>
    <a href="#features" class="nav-link">FEATURES</a>
    <a href="#modes" class="nav-link">MODES</a>
  </div>
  <a href="/login" class="nav-login">LOGIN</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-visual">
    <div class="float-card fc1">
      <div class="fc-label">SCORE UPDATE</div>
      🏆 87 / 100
    </div>
    <div class="float-card fc2">
      <div class="fc-label">ARIA-3 ASKING</div>
      "Explain your DB schema..."
    </div>
    <div class="float-card fc3">
      <div class="fc-label">TOPIC DETECTED</div>
      ⚡ Node.js · Auth · REST API
    </div>
    <div class="float-card fc4">
      <div class="fc-label">CONFIDENCE</div>
      📈 72% — Good
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-badge">
    <div class="badge-dot"></div>
    AI-Powered · Real-Time · Free
  </div>

  <h1 class="hero-title">
    <span class="line1">CRACK YOUR NEXT</span>
    <span class="line2">TECH INTERVIEW</span>
  </h1>

  <p class="hero-sub">
    PrepSphere uses <span>ARIA-3</span>, our AI interviewer, to conduct real mock interviews based on
    <span>your actual projects</span>. Get scored, get feedback, get hired.
  </p>

  <div class="hero-ctas">
    <a href="/register" class="btn-primary">⚡ START FOR FREE</a>
    <a href="#how" class="btn-secondary">SEE HOW IT WORKS</a>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-num">3</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Interview Modes</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-num">AI</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Powered by LLaMA 3.3</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-num">∞</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Practice Sessions</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-num">100</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Point Scoring System</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section id="how">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="section-tag">// HOW IT WORKS</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">From Zero to Interview-Ready<br/>in 3 Steps</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">No setup needed. Just paste your GitHub project URL and ARIA-3 does the rest.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="how-grid">
      <div class="step-card reveal">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <div class="step-icon">🔗</div>
        <div class="step-title">PASTE YOUR PROJECT</div>
        <p class="step-desc">Drop in your GitHub repository URL. ARIA-3 scrapes the README, analyses your tech stack, and builds a custom question set around your actual work.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card reveal" style="transition-delay:0.1s">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <div class="step-icon">🤖</div>
        <div class="step-title">GET INTERVIEWED BY AI</div>
        <p class="step-desc">ARIA-3 asks technical and HR questions tailored to your project. Voice input, real-time nudges, and difficulty auto-detection keep you on your toes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card reveal" style="transition-delay:0.2s">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <div class="step-icon">📊</div>
        <div class="step-title">SCORE &amp; IMPROVE</div>
        <p class="step-desc">Get a detailed score out of 100, confidence rating, improvement areas, and a downloadable PDF report. Track your progress on the dashboard.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section id="features">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="features-wrap">
      <div>
        <div class="reveal">
          <div class="section-tag">// FEATURES</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Everything You Need to Prepare</h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Built for CS students and early-career developers who want real practice, not just flashcards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-list" style="margin-top:40px">
          <div class="feature-item reveal">
            <div class="feature-icon">🧠</div>
            <div>
              <div class="feature-title">GROQ AI — LLAMA 3.3 70B</div>
              <p class="feature-desc">Industry-grade LLM powering every interview. Understands your project context deeply and asks questions a real interviewer would ask.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item reveal" style="transition-delay:0.1s">
            <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
            <div>
              <div class="feature-title">AUTO DIFFICULTY DETECTION</div>
              <p class="feature-desc">ARIA-3 reads your project and auto-detects whether to ask beginner, intermediate, or advanced questions — or you can set it manually.</p>
